info.name: Chez 3-Seater Sofa
info.description: Upholstered in regal blue Warwick Liam fabric, the Chez sofa features a plush look and feel through its sumptuous texture, tapered timber legs and elegant curving armrests. Available as a 2-seater and 3-seater sofa configuration.The Chez sofa is made in Australia and features a pine timber frame and top quality Warwick upholstery.
